    "body": "**Description of the problem**\r\n\r\nThe docs says:\r\n> -C: Settings specified under begin directive apply to all subplots, while settings under set only apply to the selected (active) subplot.\r\n\r\nSee the script below. `-Ce2c` in `subplot begin` has no effects. Adding `-Ce2c` to each `subplot set` works well.\r\n\r\n```\r\ngmt begin map\r\ngmt subplot begin 2x2 -Fs5c/4.5c+d -A -Ce2c\r\n    gmt subplot set 0\r\n    gmt grdimage @earth_relief_60m -Cgeo -JH?\r\n    gmt colorbar -DJMR -B\r\n\r\n    gmt subplot set 1\r\n    gmt grdimage @earth_relief_60m -Cgeo -JH?\r\n    gmt colorbar -DJMR -B\r\n\r\n    gmt subplot set 2\r\n    gmt grdimage @earth_relief_60m -Cgeo -JH?\r\n    gmt colorbar -DJMR -B\r\n\r\n    gmt subplot set 3\r\n    gmt grdimage @earth_relief_60m -Cgeo -JH?\r\n    gmt colorbar -DJMR -B\r\ngmt subplot end\r\ngmt end show\r\n```",
