            "body": "**subplot begin -C** works for subplots activated by **subplot set**\r\n```\r\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\r\ngmt begin subplot pdf\r\n    gmt subplot begin 2x2 -Fs5c/5c+d -Ce2c\r\n        gmt subplot set 0\r\n        gmt basemap -R0/5/0/5 -Baf\r\n        gmt subplot set 1\r\n        gmt basemap -R0/5/0/5 -Baf\r\n        gmt subplot set 2\r\n        gmt basemap -R0/5/0/5 -Baf\r\n        gmt subplot set 3\r\n        gmt basemap -R0/5/0/5 -Baf\r\n    gmt subplot end\r\ngmt end show\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut it doesn't work with **-c** option:\r\n```\r\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\r\ngmt begin subplot pdf\r\n    gmt subplot begin 2x2 -Fs5c/5c+d -Ce2c\r\n        gmt basemap -R0/5/0/5 -Baf -c\r\n        gmt basemap -R0/5/0/5 -Baf -c\r\n        gmt basemap -R0/5/0/5 -Baf -c\r\n        gmt basemap -R0/5/0/5 -Baf -c\r\n    gmt subplot end\r\ngmt end show\r\n```",
